Package: elad-spectrum
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Elad FDM-DUO SDR spectrum analyzer
 A GTK4-based spectrum analyzer and waterfall display for the
 Elad FDM-DUO Software Defined Radio transceiver.
 .
 Features:
  - Live spectrum display with FFT processing
  - Waterfall display
  - CAT control for frequency and mode display
  - Support for 192 kHz to 6144 kHz sample rates
